WEBVTT

01:36.930 --> 01:40.960
[The Best Thing]

01:41.539 --> 01:48.620
[Episode 17 Artemisia capillaris has a bitter and pungent taste with a slightly cold nature. It enters the spleen, stomach, liver, and gallbladder meridians. Its actions include clearing damp-heat, promoting bile flow, and reducing jaundice.]

01:50.250 --> 01:51.430
You're not gonna submit your homework today?

02:08.479 --> 02:09.570
Is she asleep?

02:10.639 --> 02:12.200
She's been working so hard lately again?

02:15.270 --> 02:16.590
Have a good dream.

02:34.329 --> 02:36.120
If possible,

02:36.710 --> 02:39.630
I also hope you can recover faster.

02:41.340 --> 02:43.150
Xifan, when do you get off work?

02:43.170 --> 02:44.480
Let me give you a ride.

02:47.760 --> 02:50.079
Since you flirted with me first,

02:50.550 --> 02:52.390
you should be responsible for me.

02:52.960 --> 02:54.400
You can't just walk away.

02:56.190 --> 02:57.000
Xifan,

02:57.230 --> 02:58.700
let's get back together.

03:03.980 --> 03:04.740
Xifan,

03:06.740 --> 03:07.860
let's get back together.

03:08.550 --> 03:11.510
Go away. Go away!

03:13.200 --> 03:14.270
Shen Xifan.

03:28.860 --> 03:31.270
[Red beans]

04:27.550 --> 04:28.950
You're not gonna submit your homework today?

04:39.210 --> 04:40.130
I'll

04:40.870 --> 04:42.470
submit it to you tomorrow.

05:50.550 --> 05:51.350
Dad.

05:52.040 --> 05:54.720
How is your work in Hang City going?

05:55.390 --> 05:56.390
Proceeding normally.

05:56.590 --> 05:57.870
I'll go have a look in the park this afternoon.

05:58.990 --> 06:00.930
Handle the work as you see fit.

06:01.310 --> 06:02.720
Come back when you're done there.

06:03.050 --> 06:04.370
Don't stay in Hang City.

06:04.640 --> 06:05.720
Don't worry.

06:05.950 --> 06:06.860
When the time is right,

06:06.880 --> 06:08.530
I'll go back with Shen Xifan.

06:09.250 --> 06:10.010
Yan Heng,

06:10.760 --> 06:12.230
I advise you to think carefully.

06:12.430 --> 06:13.670
Without my support,

06:13.690 --> 06:16.300
do you really think your company can run normally?

06:17.030 --> 06:18.080
We'll see.

06:23.320 --> 06:24.270
Alright, I'm hanging up.

06:24.270 --> 06:24.890
Yan Heng,

06:25.320 --> 06:27.450
know your place.

06:27.830 --> 06:29.680
You're disobeying me for Shen Xifan.

06:32.430 --> 06:33.990
Mr. Yan, the flowers you asked for are ready.

06:34.080 --> 06:34.880
But there's a traffic jam.

06:34.880 --> 06:36.030
We need to leave as soon as possible.

06:39.690 --> 06:41.720
Ask a waiter to put them in front of her office.

07:15.140 --> 07:16.030
Xifan,

07:16.390 --> 07:17.200
I'm sorry

07:17.630 --> 07:19.180
for causing you trouble yesterday.

07:50.159 --> 07:52.520
Submitting my homework during the lunch break.

08:10.910 --> 08:11.790
Red bean water?

08:15.030 --> 08:15.680
Yes.

08:22.370 --> 08:23.570
Did you buy it outside?

08:24.350 --> 08:26.550
Freshly brewed wouldn't be this clear.

08:38.880 --> 08:41.280
You really have sharp eyes.

08:49.470 --> 08:50.680
Unqualified.

08:51.680 --> 08:54.560
Come to my place tonight for a remedial session.

09:16.240 --> 09:19.200
Maybe another day. I have something to do today.

09:26.750 --> 09:27.680
Okay.

09:28.710 --> 09:29.830
Let's meet another day.

10:07.470 --> 10:09.470
Luckily, Mr. Yan went out to work today.

10:09.490 --> 10:11.210
That has saved us a lot of trouble in the hotel.

10:11.590 --> 10:13.400
Getting off work peacefully!

10:16.320 --> 10:17.320
How long has it been?

10:17.320 --> 10:18.470
Does it still have any smell?

10:18.470 --> 10:19.800
A little.

10:19.800 --> 10:20.440
What kind of smell?

10:20.440 --> 10:21.400
Let me smell it.

10:22.630 --> 10:24.990
Why don't you ask him for a new one?

10:24.990 --> 10:26.680
I haven't had time to see him lately.

10:27.630 --> 10:28.870
What's going on?

11:05.960 --> 11:06.680
Xifan.

11:08.930 --> 11:10.600
Mr. Yan, don't you need to work?

11:10.620 --> 11:11.590
You are so free.

11:12.160 --> 11:13.470
I just rushed back from a meeting.

11:14.160 --> 11:15.330
Let's have dinner together.

11:15.350 --> 11:16.300
No need.

11:20.800 --> 11:21.590
I heard

11:22.280 --> 11:23.800
you were punished for what happened yesterday.

11:24.990 --> 11:26.080
It's all my fault.

11:27.160 --> 11:28.350
Give me a chance to make it up.

11:28.690 --> 11:29.930
What good is an apology?

11:30.630 --> 11:31.960
Why don't you reimburse her

11:31.960 --> 11:32.830
deducted bonus first?

11:38.750 --> 11:39.710
Have dinner, right?

11:39.970 --> 11:41.000
I'll go with you.

11:43.190 --> 11:44.950
Staying here will only complicate things.

11:48.320 --> 11:49.200
Don't worry.

11:52.330 --> 11:53.040
Let's go.

13:14.370 --> 13:16.090
You haven't been back to the campus for a long time, right?

13:17.510 --> 13:18.750
I've never come back

13:18.750 --> 13:19.870
since you graduated.

13:21.510 --> 13:22.750
Didn't you ask me to eat with you?

13:24.470 --> 13:25.560
Isn't it good to revisit an old place?

13:26.830 --> 13:28.560
But things have changed.

13:32.090 --> 13:34.280
Mr. Yan, Manager Shen, here is your food.

13:38.740 --> 13:39.660
Eat.

13:40.120 --> 13:41.810
It's the grilled meat we used to eat.

13:45.680 --> 13:46.680
I'll eat then.

13:51.280 --> 13:52.800
How time flies.

13:53.830 --> 13:54.960
When we first met,

13:55.880 --> 13:56.910
you were only 19.

13:57.470 --> 13:58.510
I was 21.

14:06.710 --> 14:07.860
You're here. Let's go.

14:07.960 --> 14:08.560
What's wrong?

14:08.560 --> 14:09.400
Why are you covering your face?

14:10.690 --> 14:12.100
I had Thai curry shrimps tonight.

14:12.160 --> 14:13.400
I was allergic to the mango in the meat.

14:18.920 --> 14:20.680
You're so ugly.

14:20.680 --> 14:21.980
You think I'm ugly, huh?

14:22.200 --> 14:22.710
No!

14:39.950 --> 14:41.590
[Dad]

14:44.800 --> 14:45.680
You're not gonna answer it?

14:48.250 --> 14:49.920
It's from my dad. No need to answer it.

14:54.470 --> 14:57.160
Actually, Mr. Yan never really likes me.

14:59.070 --> 15:00.540
You knew that, right?

15:08.800 --> 15:09.830
So you knew.

15:12.920 --> 15:14.470
Then why did you come to me?

15:25.460 --> 15:26.540
I want to marry you.

15:31.470 --> 15:32.710
I understand my dad.

15:33.560 --> 15:34.400
He's a businessman.

15:35.280 --> 15:36.590
He wants me to marry a lady

15:36.590 --> 15:37.460
from a rich family.

15:37.520 --> 15:38.520
But I don't want to.

15:38.900 --> 15:40.950
Xifan, in this matter,

15:40.980 --> 15:42.730
you can completely ignore what he said.

15:43.230 --> 15:44.450
I'm independent now.

15:44.620 --> 15:45.570
I have my own voice.

15:46.160 --> 15:47.590
He can't decide my life anymore.

15:48.280 --> 15:50.230
My robot company has applied for many patents

15:50.230 --> 15:51.350
and won many awards.

15:51.770 --> 15:53.140
It's been acquired by Zhongyu,

15:53.440 --> 15:55.200
but I retain full control.

15:55.200 --> 15:56.200
I can contend against him.

15:56.350 --> 15:57.280
So?

15:58.200 --> 15:59.230
So he has no right

15:59.230 --> 16:00.470
to object to our marriage.

16:00.630 --> 16:02.320
But I don't want to marry you.

16:02.690 --> 16:03.290
Why?

16:04.200 --> 16:05.400
There's no why.

16:06.230 --> 16:07.400
Because I don't want to.

16:07.710 --> 16:09.470
I don't want to marry you.

16:12.230 --> 16:12.870
Xifan,

16:13.400 --> 16:15.080
I know you are still mad at me.

16:15.080 --> 16:16.350
But I already explained to you.

16:16.350 --> 16:17.440
At that time, I was too busy

16:17.440 --> 16:18.320
and too stressed

16:18.640 --> 16:19.680
to focus on us.

16:19.920 --> 16:21.280
And I'm not saying we should

16:21.280 --> 16:22.080
get married immediately.

16:22.080 --> 16:22.560
I just...

16:22.560 --> 16:23.350
You just want to get back together,

16:23.350 --> 16:24.230
right?

16:25.680 --> 16:26.400
Yan Heng,

16:27.160 --> 16:29.250
you never care about what I want.

16:29.630 --> 16:31.280
You always ask me to cooperate with you.

16:31.680 --> 16:32.870
Whether it's our breakup

16:32.870 --> 16:34.470
or your sudden appearance this time,

16:35.230 --> 16:37.140
you've never cared about my feelings,

16:37.160 --> 16:38.250
even just a little.

16:40.710 --> 16:41.870
I really don't want to marry you.

16:41.870 --> 16:43.110
And I don't want to see you anymore.

16:43.110 --> 16:44.480
Please don't come to me again!

16:45.960 --> 16:46.470
Xifan.

16:46.470 --> 16:47.400
And you know what?

16:48.280 --> 16:49.320
Since college,

16:49.320 --> 16:50.680
I've never liked grilled meat.

17:35.790 --> 17:37.140
Where's the sachet?

17:39.600 --> 17:41.120
Why is it gone?

17:49.710 --> 17:51.120
Don't think you're not good.

17:51.120 --> 17:52.750
And don't think you're worthless.

17:53.400 --> 17:55.290
You're just hurt

17:55.320 --> 17:56.600
by a bad relationship.

17:57.050 --> 17:58.160
The most important thing

17:58.600 --> 18:00.880
is to love yourself and live well.

18:33.510 --> 18:34.660
He Suye.

18:38.820 --> 18:39.740
What's wrong?

18:40.160 --> 18:41.050
Where are you?

18:41.440 --> 18:42.990
I'm on my way home.

18:44.030 --> 18:45.790
I have a headache.

18:46.790 --> 18:48.550
Can you come to take a look at me?

18:49.510 --> 18:50.030
Okay.

18:50.550 --> 18:51.510
Wait for me in the clinic.

18:51.750 --> 18:52.270
Okay.

20:25.950 --> 20:28.560
[TCM Clinic No. 3]

20:54.470 --> 20:55.600
Restless mind.

20:55.990 --> 20:57.120
Unstable qi in your liver.

20:57.710 --> 20:58.920
Stagnant qi in your heart.

21:05.270 --> 21:06.230
Ex-boyfriend trouble?

21:24.790 --> 21:25.750
Go lie down.

21:26.850 --> 21:28.010
I'll give you acupuncture.

21:28.030 --> 21:29.350
Have a good sleep tonight.

21:33.070 --> 21:33.710
Okay.

22:18.910 --> 22:19.740
Hello.

22:19.920 --> 22:21.400
We're closing.

22:21.430 --> 22:23.160
Are you here for medicine or treatment?

22:26.500 --> 22:27.210
I'm looking for someone.

22:36.340 --> 22:37.340
Are you feeling better?

22:39.440 --> 22:40.440
Much better.

22:41.300 --> 22:42.740
My head doesn't hurt that much.

22:47.840 --> 22:48.750
Then...

22:49.470 --> 22:50.700
can you tell me

22:50.870 --> 22:52.430
what on earth happened tonight?

23:06.550 --> 23:07.550
He Suye.

23:09.780 --> 23:10.690
I...

23:18.470 --> 23:19.120
It's okay.

23:19.790 --> 23:20.520
Lie down.

23:32.600 --> 23:34.120
Mr. Yan, are you here for treatment?

23:35.110 --> 23:36.380
Let me take your pulse.

23:36.690 --> 23:37.380
It's free.

23:37.410 --> 23:37.930
No need.

23:38.560 --> 23:40.430
I'd never seek treatment in a place like this.

23:42.400 --> 23:43.470
I'm here to accompany her.

23:44.110 --> 23:45.850
She's throwing a tantrum at me.

23:46.340 --> 23:47.820
The acupuncture treatment takes 15 minutes.

23:48.020 --> 23:49.220
Mr. Yan, you should

23:49.840 --> 23:51.070
have a seat and wait for her.

23:59.010 --> 24:00.920
Fifteen minutes. I'll wait.

24:05.290 --> 24:06.960
Xifan, I'll be waiting for you outside.

24:10.130 --> 24:11.160
Be patient.

24:11.680 --> 24:13.720
Patients need quiet.

24:14.690 --> 24:15.580
Otherwise,

24:15.610 --> 24:17.960
blood might spurt from the needles.

24:21.880 --> 24:22.640
Fifteen minutes.

24:53.970 --> 24:54.970
It's done, right?

24:55.000 --> 24:56.440
Let's go. I'll drive you home.

24:56.460 --> 24:57.700
She still needs moxibustion.

24:57.840 --> 24:59.680
Why don't you go to the toilet first?

24:59.970 --> 25:01.410
Moxibustion will take more than 20 minutes.

25:03.770 --> 25:05.630
Okay, I'll listen to you.

25:13.380 --> 25:14.970
Mr. Yan, you don't need to go with her.

25:16.190 --> 25:19.390
It's not proper to go to the toilet with a woman.

25:20.710 --> 25:21.970
You're being so nosy.

25:23.890 --> 25:24.860
Dr. He, right?

25:25.920 --> 25:26.760
Let me remind you.

25:27.990 --> 25:29.030
Stop wasting your effort.

25:29.030 --> 25:30.200
She won't fall for your tricks.

25:30.880 --> 25:32.360
You must have pursued her for a long time.

25:32.770 --> 25:34.050
If she fell for your tricks,

25:34.510 --> 25:35.920
she would have been your girlfriend long ago, right?

25:36.960 --> 25:38.330
We were lovers for seven years.

25:38.790 --> 25:40.160
We were about to get married.

25:40.520 --> 25:41.470
I know her too well.

25:43.370 --> 25:45.160
It's just like artemisia capillaris in April.

25:47.920 --> 25:48.710
What does that mean?

25:49.160 --> 25:49.960
Are you cursing me?

25:50.560 --> 25:51.230
No.

25:52.470 --> 25:54.260
You can google it.

25:56.510 --> 25:57.470
You are just a back-up,

25:57.470 --> 25:58.960
but you've been trying so hard.

25:59.350 --> 26:01.270
That's because you're not good enough.

26:01.640 --> 26:02.710
I'm still in the game.

26:02.710 --> 26:03.560
You won't have a chance.

26:05.340 --> 26:08.060
Really? I thought she dumped you long ago.

26:12.040 --> 26:13.910
Mr. Yan, you still won't leave?

26:14.270 --> 26:15.360
I'm getting off work.

26:18.480 --> 26:20.200
Xifan has left.

26:42.110 --> 26:42.900
Mr. Yan.

26:45.610 --> 26:46.890
Have you seen Shen Xifan?

26:47.370 --> 26:48.030
No.

27:21.400 --> 27:22.570
Why are you sitting on the ground?

27:22.600 --> 27:23.560
Get up.

27:26.960 --> 27:28.050
Your hands are so cold.

27:28.810 --> 27:30.050
Come on. Put on my coat.

27:31.190 --> 27:37.550
♫The moment I see you, all my worries turn transparent♫

27:36.550 --> 27:37.200
Are you cold?

27:38.360 --> 27:45.680
♫In the silence, the sound of my heartbeat grows clearer♫

27:45.740 --> 27:50.980
♫The entire world reflects in your eyes♫

27:51.120 --> 27:59.970
♫Make a wish, can the snow fall slowly?♫

28:00.340 --> 28:03.980
♫Even if we're destined to meet and miss each other♫

28:04.000 --> 28:10.160
♫Life is finally complete♫

28:08.160 --> 28:09.160
Xifan.

28:12.270 --> 28:13.920
Why can't you let him go?

28:19.230 --> 28:21.190
It's not that I can't let him go.

28:24.960 --> 28:27.980
I'm just mad at my past self.

28:33.720 --> 28:35.200
No matter what happened in the past,

28:36.210 --> 28:37.650
good or bad,

28:39.120 --> 28:41.010
it's part of who you are.

28:44.070 --> 28:45.270
Accept the past,

28:46.570 --> 28:49.400
and focus on the present and the future.

28:59.730 --> 29:00.620
Besides,

29:02.270 --> 29:03.400
think from this perspective:

29:04.270 --> 29:05.430
without him,

29:06.770 --> 29:08.530
you wouldn't have come to the clinic

29:08.560 --> 29:10.120
because of insomnia.

29:10.550 --> 29:11.400
Right?

29:14.740 --> 29:15.740
Good.

29:20.710 --> 29:21.400
Stop crying.

29:23.880 --> 29:24.880
Unknowingly,

29:25.200 --> 29:26.730
I've treated you for so long.

29:28.030 --> 29:29.360
You're finally healing.

29:38.180 --> 29:41.680
♫Watching the snow fall, flake by flake♫

29:41.700 --> 29:45.320
♫Slowly melting away my thoughts♫

29:43.550 --> 29:44.440
You're not cold now, right?

29:45.340 --> 29:48.600
♫Smiling, I wave goodbye as you head home♫

29:46.640 --> 29:47.640
Go back now.

29:48.030 --> 29:49.120
It's a bit cold beside the river.

29:49.120 --> 29:49.710
Don't catch a cold.

29:49.160 --> 29:52.440
♫But I never said those words♫

29:52.530 --> 29:56.050
♫Flake by flake, the snow melts♫

29:56.130 --> 29:59.930
♫Love blooms quietly♫

30:00.080 --> 30:06.070
♫Hold you close with a kiss♫

30:06.090 --> 30:09.930
♫White lovers are whispering♫

30:12.400 --> 30:14.840
Keep your wrist steady, and press hard.

30:15.450 --> 30:17.040
She's back. Our daughter is back.

30:17.360 --> 30:17.960
You're back.

30:18.780 --> 30:20.130
Why are you back so late?

30:21.270 --> 30:22.470
I worked overtime today.

30:22.470 --> 30:23.470
Are you hungry?

30:27.850 --> 30:29.330
I made Red Bean Soup with Tangerine Peel.

30:29.360 --> 30:31.190
Do you want me to heat it up for you?

30:32.400 --> 30:33.830
I'm not hungry.

30:34.030 --> 30:35.470
I want to take a shower and go to bed.

30:35.470 --> 30:36.510
That tired?

30:36.790 --> 30:38.200
Why did you work overtime?

30:38.640 --> 30:39.790
There was a big event?

30:41.070 --> 30:42.360
No.

30:42.920 --> 30:43.960
I just...

30:44.310 --> 30:46.310
met a difficult VIP client.

30:46.880 --> 30:49.070
Who is that difficult?

30:49.510 --> 30:51.840
I think you should go to a TCM physician again.

30:52.830 --> 30:54.190
You don't have to go to He.

30:54.210 --> 30:55.760
You can get another doctor.

30:59.200 --> 31:00.070
Maybe later.

31:00.270 --> 31:00.750
Dad.

31:01.120 --> 31:02.070
Help me hang the keys.

31:02.070 --> 31:03.030
I'm going back to my room.

31:09.290 --> 31:12.160
Do you think she looks weird

31:12.160 --> 31:13.360
whenever we mention He?

31:14.400 --> 31:15.400
A little.

31:15.850 --> 31:17.000
A little?

31:17.030 --> 31:18.400
It's so obvious.

31:21.230 --> 31:22.200
Shen,

31:23.550 --> 31:25.030
you should resolve the situation

31:26.090 --> 31:27.370
with Mr. Yan as soon as possible.

31:28.960 --> 31:30.920
He came to you frequently and publicly.

31:31.510 --> 31:32.920
It's really not good.

31:33.810 --> 31:35.400
After all, gossip is a fearful thing.

31:36.470 --> 31:39.470
In our industry, we're already walking on thin ice.

31:40.360 --> 31:42.510
Every hotel has staff

31:42.510 --> 31:45.620
fired for being involved with guests.

31:46.440 --> 31:48.530
If you're dismissed over something like this,

31:48.840 --> 31:51.370
it'll be hard for you to continue your career

31:51.580 --> 31:52.660
in the hotel industry.

31:55.990 --> 31:57.120
I understand.

31:58.020 --> 32:00.440
[Meeting Hall]

31:59.290 --> 32:00.570
You're still young.

32:00.590 --> 32:02.140
You have a brilliant future.

32:02.790 --> 32:05.220
Don't let this ruin it.

32:07.960 --> 32:09.640
General Manager, thank you for your advice.

32:10.440 --> 32:11.770
I will solve it as soon as possible.

32:12.920 --> 32:13.470
My apologies

32:14.400 --> 32:15.470
for the trouble.

32:15.880 --> 32:16.840
That's all.

32:16.920 --> 32:17.850
Go back to work.

32:20.250 --> 32:21.200
Thank you, General Manager.

32:45.800 --> 32:47.670
I'll ask my dad to pick it up after work.

33:30.440 --> 33:30.960
Hello.

33:31.310 --> 33:31.750
Hello.

33:34.000 --> 33:35.130
Did you sleep well last night?

33:36.040 --> 33:38.080
Yes, pretty well.

33:41.840 --> 33:42.960
The guy last night...

33:44.450 --> 33:45.890
When will he check out?

33:47.990 --> 33:49.680
Perhaps in a week or two.

33:56.070 --> 33:57.070
If you have any issues,

33:57.070 --> 33:58.510
feel free to call me anytime.

33:59.230 --> 33:59.960
No problem.

34:03.200 --> 34:04.400
They need me for a meeting.

34:04.400 --> 34:05.360
I'm hanging up.

34:06.330 --> 34:07.050
Okay.

34:07.470 --> 34:09.719
Then... keep in touch.

34:09.989 --> 34:10.570
Okay.

34:11.400 --> 34:12.440
Bye bye.

34:12.889 --> 34:13.520
See you.

34:33.670 --> 34:35.830
Make sure the rest area's tea

34:36.219 --> 34:37.090
and refreshments are enough.

34:37.120 --> 34:38.480
Okay. Got it.

34:43.480 --> 34:44.170
Okay.

34:49.480 --> 34:50.679
[Yuncong All Day Dining Restaurant]

34:56.800 --> 34:57.470
Good afternoon.

35:04.130 --> 35:07.520
[Manager of Front Office]

35:16.660 --> 35:17.700
Are you looking for me?

35:18.920 --> 35:19.720
Manager Shen.

35:20.240 --> 35:21.150
Mr. Yan has been busy

35:21.150 --> 35:22.780
negotiating the economic park collaboration these days.

35:22.810 --> 35:23.730
He's been in and out at all hours,

35:23.800 --> 35:25.110
so he asked me to deliver these flowers.

35:25.110 --> 35:26.470
No need to deliver flowers anymore in the future.

35:26.760 --> 35:27.990
I've thrown away the previous ones.

35:28.570 --> 35:29.740
You don't have to accept them,

35:29.770 --> 35:32.120
but I have to fulfill Mr. Yan's instructions.

35:32.140 --> 35:33.980
Then please tell Mr. Yan

35:34.150 --> 35:35.340
to stop delivering flowers.

35:37.530 --> 35:39.580
Why don't you tell Mr. Yan yourself?

35:39.630 --> 35:41.580
I no longer have his contact information.

35:42.100 --> 35:42.960
Thank you.

36:01.110 --> 36:01.880
It's not spring yet.

36:01.880 --> 36:03.160
The lingering chill is a bit strong.

36:03.210 --> 36:04.560
I've prescribed two warming tonics for you

36:04.590 --> 36:05.410
to regulate your spleen and stomach.

36:05.920 --> 36:06.920
Try them.

36:07.150 --> 36:07.750
Okay.

36:15.840 --> 36:16.590
Auntie,

36:16.920 --> 36:19.110
the most important thing is to stay in a good mood.

36:19.110 --> 36:21.510
Don't let anything weigh on your mind.

36:23.110 --> 36:25.400
I happen to have something weighing on my mind these days.

36:26.400 --> 36:27.110
Dr. He,

36:27.110 --> 36:28.150
you know what?

36:28.440 --> 36:30.560
A terrible person showed up in the hotel.

36:31.360 --> 36:32.550
It has made Xifan

36:32.990 --> 36:34.030
very passive

36:34.680 --> 36:35.920
and uncomfortable.

36:39.320 --> 36:40.360
I know that person.

36:40.550 --> 36:41.880
I saw him last night.

36:42.800 --> 36:45.320
And today, Xifan suddenly asked me

36:45.340 --> 36:46.790
if he came to me.

36:46.890 --> 36:47.890
It's strange.

36:48.570 --> 36:50.570
Did he do something in the hotel?

36:51.800 --> 36:53.640
Once, I saw him

36:53.770 --> 36:56.080
forcing Xifan to meet him.

36:56.150 --> 36:57.760
It was quite a scene.

36:58.670 --> 37:02.670
I heard Xifan got punished because of it.

37:05.540 --> 37:07.060
He came again yesterday,

37:07.480 --> 37:09.520
and forced her to go with him.

37:10.360 --> 37:11.590
I think Xifan

37:11.910 --> 37:13.910
has been in a bad mood these days.

37:14.540 --> 37:15.730
She looks very haggard.

37:16.320 --> 37:18.070
Auntie, don't worry.

37:18.070 --> 37:19.470
I understand what you mean.

37:20.510 --> 37:21.470
Xifan

37:21.960 --> 37:23.070
is not a girl

37:23.070 --> 37:24.990
who easily opens her heart.

37:25.800 --> 37:27.240
So I don't really dare to interfere

37:27.470 --> 37:29.030
too much in her personal matters.

37:30.550 --> 37:32.590
Besides, she's a smart person.

37:33.590 --> 37:35.360
She's just been a little lost recently.

37:37.800 --> 37:38.630
I think things will be fine soon.

37:39.880 --> 37:40.770
Soon,

37:40.800 --> 37:42.070
spring will arrive.

37:49.290 --> 37:51.400
Take this prescription to get the medicine.

37:52.840 --> 37:53.440
Thank you.

37:53.440 --> 37:54.110
No big deal.

37:55.030 --> 37:56.110
Stay in a good mood.

37:56.440 --> 37:57.780
Okay, thank you.

38:10.880 --> 38:13.910
[Signing Ceremony]

38:29.300 --> 38:31.070
He looks polished.

38:41.140 --> 38:41.940
It's salty.

38:42.960 --> 38:43.990
Have something sweet.

38:50.000 --> 38:50.690
Too salty.

38:52.110 --> 38:52.800
Balance it out.

39:04.130 --> 39:04.840
500 million yuan?

39:09.030 --> 39:10.550
So he's a domineering president.

39:11.600 --> 39:12.400
What domineering president?

39:12.880 --> 39:13.470
Who is a domineering president?

39:14.320 --> 39:14.960
Suye!

39:15.670 --> 39:17.550
The research project has been approved!

39:19.110 --> 39:21.240
We've got the support fund from the hospital.

39:21.440 --> 39:22.240
Look.

39:29.210 --> 39:30.000
Great.

39:30.840 --> 39:31.570
Take a photo.

39:31.810 --> 39:33.190
Not bad.

39:42.070 --> 39:42.630
So,

39:42.840 --> 39:45.390
will you take on this research project again this year?

39:45.630 --> 39:46.670
Of course.

39:47.030 --> 39:48.880
I spent half a year on it last year.

39:49.060 --> 39:50.230
I must do it well.

39:51.400 --> 39:52.190
Congratulations.

39:52.960 --> 39:53.760
You've been working on

39:53.760 --> 39:56.440
the palliative care topic for over two years.

39:57.290 --> 40:00.040
Hard work pays off.

40:00.150 --> 40:02.760
Why does that sound like a backhanded compliment?

40:02.760 --> 40:03.970
How so?

40:04.850 --> 40:05.930
I also heard

40:06.070 --> 40:09.360
our country will step up efforts to support TCM this year.

40:09.360 --> 40:10.030
Soon,

40:10.190 --> 40:11.030
there'll be provincial

40:11.030 --> 40:13.510
and national-level research projects to apply for.

40:14.670 --> 40:15.550
Where did you hear that?

40:15.890 --> 40:16.860
Reliable sources.

40:17.400 --> 40:19.670
I think it will be announced in a few days.

40:20.170 --> 40:22.080
And I've seen your research project.

40:22.380 --> 40:23.340
It's new,

40:23.400 --> 40:25.400
but it's very valuable in this era.

40:25.550 --> 40:26.720
It's got potential.

40:27.030 --> 40:28.800
It's better than the common research projects

40:28.800 --> 40:30.320
of other hospitals

40:30.320 --> 40:31.150
and schools.

40:31.340 --> 40:34.660
I think it's very likely that it'll get approved.

40:36.150 --> 40:37.190
Now that's what I like to hear.

40:37.190 --> 40:37.800
Right?

40:38.240 --> 40:38.630
Alright.

40:38.630 --> 40:39.780
Let's hope so.

40:39.990 --> 40:41.410
If it really gets approved,

40:41.550 --> 40:42.590
I'll treat you two to a meal.

40:42.590 --> 40:44.840
How about this? I'll say more auspicious words.

40:44.840 --> 40:46.590
Treat me to five meals, okay?

40:47.550 --> 40:49.070
You shouldn't be a doctor.

40:49.070 --> 40:50.070
You should be a wedding emcee.

40:50.070 --> 40:50.760
To be honest,

40:50.760 --> 40:52.030
I outshine any wedding emcee.

40:52.030 --> 40:53.470
I wish you a huge success,

40:53.470 --> 40:55.110
great harmony and prosperity,

40:55.110 --> 40:56.440
bountiful blessings,

40:56.440 --> 40:57.140
and good luck.

40:57.170 --> 40:58.690
Are you going to eat?

40:58.710 --> 41:00.230
Take me with you. I'm a bit hungry.

41:03.960 --> 41:04.840
Of course you should be

41:04.840 --> 41:06.880
the first one to know such good news.

41:07.950 --> 41:09.340
That's more like it.

41:10.190 --> 41:11.110
Keep it up.

41:11.310 --> 41:12.580
You're young and inexperienced,

41:12.600 --> 41:14.770
but you've managed to finish a research project.

41:15.150 --> 41:16.360
Quite impressive.

41:16.740 --> 41:18.050
When you become successful in the future,

41:18.150 --> 41:19.990
your mother would be pleased

41:19.990 --> 41:21.670
in heaven.

41:22.410 --> 41:24.360
Alright, that's all for now.

41:24.640 --> 41:25.880
Take care.

41:26.440 --> 41:26.960
Bye bye.

41:27.470 --> 41:28.150
Bye bye.

41:53.980 --> 41:55.230
The weather is nice today.
